What?

00:22:21.694 --> 00:22:22.612
Hey!

00:22:22.631 --> 00:22:24.411
I sent the wrong message because of you!

00:22:25.791 --> 00:22:26.906
So what?

00:22:27.547 --> 00:22:28.622
What?

00:22:44.941 --> 00:22:47.556
When did you put that in again?

00:22:53.821 --> 00:22:55.964
The number of users has tripled.

00:22:56.889 --> 00:22:58.935
Really, our app is

00:22:59.060 --> 00:23:02.524
the hottest topic among people for days.

00:23:02.599 --> 00:23:05.932
They even made a community
just for Version 2!

00:23:05.951 --> 00:23:08.581
All the ladies around me are
only talking about this.

00:23:08.601 --> 00:23:12.104
They're debating if it's an affair
when married women use it.

00:23:12.805 --> 00:23:17.121
Isn't this all thanks to
the power of Mr. Han?

00:23:17.337 --> 00:23:18.377
Thanks to me?

00:23:18.540 --> 00:23:24.096
You could say it's because of Mr. Han,
but it's really the app's power.

00:23:59.693 --> 00:24:00.693
Gosh.

00:24:01.957 --> 00:24:03.179
What is it?

00:24:03.241 --> 00:24:04.211
Where are you going?

00:24:14.249 --> 00:24:15.324
Where are you going?

00:24:19.671 --> 00:24:20.746
Where are you going?

00:24:25.085 --> 00:24:27.460
[Director's Office]

00:24:30.690 --> 00:24:31.765
Where are you going?

00:24:39.786 --> 00:24:40.910
Where are you going?

00:24:45.581 --> 00:24:47.951
Why do you keep following me?

00:24:48.776 --> 00:24:51.011
Aren't you reassured with me by your side?

00:24:51.466 --> 00:24:52.541
A guardian angel.

00:24:54.611 --> 00:24:55.746
More like a stalker, no?

00:25:04.631 --> 00:25:06.466
How far are you going to follow me?

00:25:10.811 --> 00:25:12.286
I'm sorry, I'm sorry.

00:25:15.991 --> 00:25:17.846
Are you trying to embarrass someone?

00:25:18.618 --> 00:25:20.456
Oh look, it's almost quitting time.

00:25:21.841 --> 00:25:23.266
I'm hungry.

00:25:23.771 --> 00:25:25.201
Everyone says they have plans.

00:25:25.326 --> 00:25:27.016
Isn't there anyone to eat with?

00:25:29.691 --> 00:25:31.851
You should keep your monologues quieter.

00:25:32.416 --> 00:25:34.211
Why are you eavesdropping
on my monologue?

00:25:36.026 --> 00:25:37.101
Stalker.

00:25:59.699 --> 00:26:01.320
Goodness.

00:26:02.121 --> 00:26:02.803
Auntie!

00:26:02.823 --> 00:26:04.991
Oh, Sunho, you're here?

00:26:05.011 --> 00:26:07.261
Why haven't you visited in so long?

00:26:09.550 --> 00:26:10.550
Oh my!

00:26:10.916 --> 00:26:12.201
Girlfriend?

00:26:12.895 --> 00:26:13.625
Yes.

00:26:14.062 --> 00:26:15.062
Ouch!

00:26:15.541 --> 00:26:16.616
No.

00:26:18.531 --> 00:26:19.756
Our company's Director.

00:26:20.981 --> 00:26:22.326
You two look good together...

00:26:23.517 --> 00:26:24.382
Oh goodness.

00:26:24.401 --> 00:26:28.456
Please take good care of Sunho.

00:26:28.527 --> 00:26:32.048
He looks neat, but

00:26:32.067 --> 00:26:34.656
he can't do anything on his own.

00:26:34.916 --> 00:26:35.954
Auntie!

00:26:35.973 --> 00:26:37.290
But it's true, right?

00:26:38.311 --> 00:26:42.271
Still, isn't Sunho doing quite well?

00:26:42.415 --> 00:26:43.536
Ah, well...

00:26:43.690 --> 00:26:44.741
Yes.

00:26:44.760 --> 00:26:46.990
But why does your expression...

00:26:47.815 --> 00:26:49.008
look so bad?

00:26:49.566 --> 00:26:51.370
- Go inside, Auntie, quickly.
- Why, why?

00:26:51.490 --> 00:26:55.117
You two are so honestly well-matched.

00:26:55.136 --> 00:26:57.276
Why does everything fit so well today?

00:26:57.417 --> 00:26:59.452
[Jeong Ribs]

00:27:06.821 --> 00:27:09.148
When you have a free hour,

00:27:11.424 --> 00:27:13.416
what's the first thing you want to do?

00:27:17.300 --> 00:27:18.524
Go to the movies?

00:27:22.493 --> 00:27:23.568
Amusement park?

00:27:24.121 --> 00:27:25.196
Or...

00:27:26.011 --> 00:27:26.999
travel?

00:27:32.341 --> 00:27:33.996
I'm already doing it.

00:27:35.070 --> 00:27:36.475
Thanks to Han Sunho.

00:27:39.812 --> 00:27:40.900
I see.

00:27:43.291 --> 00:27:44.746
Going on a date with me?

00:27:48.371 --> 00:27:51.406
Working at a company like everyone else.

00:27:52.794 --> 00:27:54.718
Going to company dinners,

00:27:55.150 --> 00:27:57.386
choosing lunch menus together,

00:27:58.081 --> 00:27:59.646
having coffee.

00:28:00.341 --> 00:28:01.416
And?

00:28:01.487 --> 00:28:03.002
Is there anything else you want to do?

00:28:03.215 --> 00:28:04.326
And if there is?

00:28:04.951 --> 00:28:06.026
Then do it.

00:28:10.761 --> 00:28:13.024
It might not be a big deal to others,

00:28:14.849 --> 00:28:16.336
but it's not easy for me.

00:28:17.924 --> 00:28:19.789
You might not understand, Han Sunho.

00:28:24.471 --> 00:28:25.758
In the past,

00:28:25.991 --> 00:28:27.966
someone helped me too.

00:28:29.381 --> 00:28:31.131
Thanks to that, I didn't hide

00:28:31.956 --> 00:28:33.640
and could come out.

00:28:35.721 --> 00:28:36.947
That debt,

00:28:37.672 --> 00:28:39.356
I'm repaying to Yun Bia.

00:28:42.591 --> 00:28:43.666
So,

00:28:43.866 --> 00:28:46.121
use me to do everything
you ever wanted to try.

00:28:46.896 --> 00:28:48.521
At least until the watch is fixed.

00:28:49.176 --> 00:28:51.166
But why are you telling me this?

00:28:52.981 --> 00:28:54.056
That's...

00:29:02.271 --> 00:29:03.346
A secret.

00:29:07.944 --> 00:29:09.019
Auntie,

00:29:09.135 --> 00:29:10.226
thank you for the meal.

00:29:11.998 --> 00:29:13.786
Take care.

00:29:13.805 --> 00:29:15.346
He really...

00:29:21.561 --> 00:29:22.876
Hey, Han Sunho!

00:29:26.761 --> 00:29:27.836
What?

00:29:28.295 --> 00:29:29.370
Han Sunho?

00:29:31.382 --> 00:29:32.816
What did you just say?

00:29:33.531 --> 00:29:34.756
Hey, Han Sunho?

00:29:37.621 --> 00:29:38.696
Don't come.

00:29:38.960 --> 00:29:40.056
Don't come!

00:29:43.501 --> 00:29:47.016
- Yun Bia, aren't you going to stop?
- I said don't come!

00:30:00.281 --> 00:30:01.516
Is your stomach okay?

00:30:02.141 --> 00:30:03.616
It's nothing to worry about...

00:30:09.111 --> 00:30:10.806
Director, you're here?

00:30:11.661 --> 00:30:13.516
- Hello.
- Hello.

00:30:15.891 --> 00:30:17.526
A package for you, sir.

00:30:18.200 --> 00:30:19.082
Okay.

00:30:19.101 --> 00:30:20.176
Thanks.

00:30:26.880 --> 00:30:27.955
Sir.

00:30:28.208 --> 00:30:30.326
Is there something you want to say?

00:30:32.601 --> 00:30:33.676
How about

00:30:33.817 --> 00:30:36.002
trying to be a bit more like
an ordinary Director this time?

00:30:36.021 --> 00:30:38.106
An ordinary Director?

00:30:38.431 --> 00:30:41.006
You could at least greet
the staff in the morning.

00:30:49.341 --> 00:30:50.958
First, lift the corners of your mouth

00:30:50.978 --> 00:30:53.437
about 30 degrees without overdoing it.

00:30:56.622 --> 00:30:58.546
And slightly close your eyes.

00:31:01.891 --> 00:31:04.006
Raise your right hand naturally.

00:31:09.571 --> 00:31:12.666
And speak in a voice about
three keys higher than usual.

00:31:14.081 --> 00:31:15.156
Good morning!

00:31:15.646 --> 00:31:19.416
Good morning, good morning, good morning.

00:31:28.753 --> 00:31:29.928
Good morning.

00:31:30.671 --> 00:31:31.746
Good morning.

00:31:31.851 --> 00:31:33.606
Did you just greet us?

00:31:34.812 --> 00:31:35.688
What's going on?

00:31:35.741 --> 00:31:37.016
He seems to be in a good mood.

00:31:44.364 --> 00:31:45.557
Ahh!

00:31:52.220 --> 00:31:54.870
It looks like there's blood on it.

00:31:55.116 --> 00:31:58.441
Why does it look so unsettling?

00:31:58.606 --> 00:32:02.676
So, this was on Jooyeon's desk, right?

00:32:02.801 --> 00:32:04.516
Didn't you see who left it?

00:32:04.568 --> 00:32:05.411
No.

00:32:05.683 --> 00:32:06.927
Not that part...

00:32:07.006 --> 00:32:09.801
Let's check the CCTV right away.

00:32:09.821 --> 00:32:11.060
I already checked,

00:32:11.120 --> 00:32:14.481
but unfortunately,
Jooyeon's desk is in a blind spot.

00:32:14.644 --> 00:32:15.719
Sul,

00:32:16.691 --> 00:32:19.701
how's the restoration of
the server room CCTV going?

00:32:20.172 --> 00:32:22.807
There was too much footage,
so only part of it was restored.

00:32:24.916 --> 00:32:25.991
Take a look at this.

00:32:32.405 --> 00:32:33.405
Hey.

00:32:33.501 --> 00:32:35.822
Isn't this when Baekho trespassed?

00:32:37.526 --> 00:32:38.524
Yes.

00:32:38.644 --> 00:32:41.776
But someone else was also
caught on the restored footage.

00:32:45.204 --> 00:32:46.098
What?

00:32:46.211 --> 00:32:47.139
Really?

00:32:47.159 --> 00:32:49.326
So someone did mess with the server room.

00:32:49.778 --> 00:32:51.493
What do the police say?

00:32:51.590 --> 00:32:53.707
Since it's confirmed someone broke in,

00:32:53.732 --> 00:32:55.826
they're turning it into
a formal investigation.

00:32:56.386 --> 00:32:58.061
Handle it quietly, if possible.

00:32:58.136 --> 00:32:59.211
Everyone,

00:32:59.624 --> 00:33:01.921
be careful not to let this leak outside.

00:33:02.368 --> 00:33:03.443
- Yes.
- Yes.

00:33:04.281 --> 00:33:04.868
Still...

00:33:04.887 --> 00:33:07.071
The response to
'ForMe Version 2' is good.

00:33:07.196 --> 00:33:09.226
We can't let this disrupt things.

00:33:11.411 --> 00:33:12.726
But,

00:33:13.332 --> 00:33:16.886
doesn't this doll seem like a message?

00:33:17.188 --> 00:33:17.889
What?

00:33:18.364 --> 00:33:19.238
I mean...

00:33:19.341 --> 00:33:22.476
It has two bodies and faces tied together,

00:33:22.601 --> 00:33:24.959
and one face is unrecognizable.

00:33:25.384 --> 00:33:27.576
It doesn't seem like just a prank.

00:33:58.980 --> 00:34:00.215
Are you okay?

00:34:01.011 --> 00:34:02.536
Haven't you left work yet?

00:34:04.390 --> 00:34:05.390
Here you go.

00:34:14.861 --> 00:34:15.861
Oh.

00:34:16.981 --> 00:34:18.465
Is it all fixed?

00:34:18.590 --> 00:34:20.405
Sorry, it took too long, right?

00:34:21.874 --> 00:34:24.590
I was too busy with
the demo release and other stuff.

00:34:25.568 --> 00:34:26.643
Thanks.

00:34:28.211 --> 00:34:29.286
Let me see.

00:34:30.601 --> 00:34:31.776
I'll do it for you.

00:34:41.450 --> 00:34:42.525
Jaehee.

00:34:45.483 --> 00:34:46.801
I'm going to try.

00:34:50.170 --> 00:34:51.720
Going without the watch.

00:34:52.758 --> 00:34:53.920
I'll give it a shot.

00:34:55.751 --> 00:34:57.896
I can't live like this forever.

00:34:59.357 --> 00:35:01.492
I think I've gotten better lately.

00:35:02.471 --> 00:35:03.846
No, it's not okay.

00:35:05.983 --> 00:35:06.945
Huh?

00:35:09.401 --> 00:35:10.959
I'm saying I'm not okay.

00:35:14.584 --> 00:35:15.659
I'm hurt.

00:35:25.784 --> 00:35:26.859
Sorry.

00:35:27.470 --> 00:35:28.936
He can't be

00:35:28.955 --> 00:35:31.456
by your side forever like I can.

00:35:36.164 --> 00:35:37.530
But for now,

00:35:39.102 --> 00:35:41.833
because of him,
you're a bit more at ease, right?

00:35:43.558 --> 00:35:44.633
Right?

00:35:46.561 --> 00:35:47.636
Yeah.

00:35:52.861 --> 00:35:54.600
Then there's no choice.

00:35:58.291 --> 00:35:59.756
Keep this safe.

00:36:00.211 --> 00:36:02.256
You never know when you might need it.

00:36:12.234 --> 00:36:13.309
Me?

00:36:13.938 --> 00:36:15.013
Why?

00:36:15.950 --> 00:36:18.424
Who else is going to look out
for Baekho if not me?

00:36:18.938 --> 00:36:20.005
Hey.

00:36:20.921 --> 00:36:21.996
San,

00:36:22.273 --> 00:36:23.290
are you lonely?

00:36:23.368 --> 00:36:24.196
What?

00:36:25.210 --> 00:36:27.400
Who's lonely? Who?

00:36:27.454 --> 00:36:30.256
Everyone either gets married
or breaks up anyway.

00:36:30.671 --> 00:36:34.526
Why put so much effort into
someone you're going to break up with?

00:36:34.581 --> 00:36:35.434
Right?

00:36:36.018 --> 00:36:37.093
San, San.

00:36:37.357 --> 00:36:38.846
Try 'ForMe' once. Wait no...

00:36:39.381 --> 00:36:41.186
meet 'ForMe' once.

00:36:41.331 --> 00:36:43.026
It's really good.

00:36:43.351 --> 00:36:44.529
Really.

00:36:46.354 --> 00:36:47.429
Is it?

00:36:48.561 --> 00:36:49.646
Eternal love.

00:36:51.181 --> 00:36:52.386
Eternal love.

00:36:54.361 --> 00:36:55.741
Aren't you guys leaving work?

00:36:55.803 --> 00:36:58.226
Ah, we still have some work left.

00:36:58.351 --> 00:37:01.166
Habitual overtime is unproductive,
you know.

00:37:08.735 --> 00:37:09.535
Wow.

00:37:09.661 --> 00:37:12.546
Sometimes, Jooyeon,
you remind me of Director Yun.

00:37:12.982 --> 00:37:13.825
Yeah.

00:37:24.951 --> 00:37:26.050
Thank you

00:37:27.401 --> 00:37:28.672
for today as well.

00:37:30.151 --> 00:37:31.577
I'll walk you to your door.

00:37:32.078 --> 00:37:33.351
It's okay.

00:37:43.891 --> 00:37:45.906
Don't worry too much.

00:37:46.041 --> 00:37:47.346
It happens sometimes.

00:37:47.941 --> 00:37:50.266
"Technology devours humanity."

00:37:50.521 --> 00:37:53.306
"We shouldn't let AI take over love too."

00:37:53.850 --> 00:37:56.965
Even religious groups call me a demon.

00:37:57.200 --> 00:37:59.765
They say I'm defying
God's will or something.

00:38:00.504 --> 00:38:02.069
But you can't be alone.

00:38:17.731 --> 00:38:19.206
Well, I'm off then.

00:38:28.794 --> 00:38:29.979
Do you want to

00:38:30.615 --> 00:38:31.979
grab something to eat?

00:38:33.198 --> 00:38:33.786
Oh!

00:38:33.841 --> 00:38:34.916
No!

00:38:36.691 --> 00:38:39.828
- I'm going home...
- You've been busy following me around.

00:38:40.469 --> 00:38:41.544
Come in.

00:39:10.804 --> 00:39:12.213
Han Sunho,

00:39:15.365 --> 00:39:16.841
is this all right?

00:39:17.566 --> 00:39:18.806
Is it okay?

00:39:19.821 --> 00:39:20.565
Yeah.

00:39:28.151 --> 00:39:29.971
I thought there'd be more...

00:39:33.169 --> 00:39:34.478
Should we order in?

00:39:34.930 --> 00:39:36.005
It's fine.

00:39:37.240 --> 00:39:38.315
What's this?

00:39:38.958 --> 00:39:39.958
Well...

00:39:40.181 --> 00:39:42.316
Jaehee fixed it, the watch.

00:39:45.557 --> 00:39:46.978
I've been curious,

00:39:48.314 --> 00:39:49.274
you two,

00:39:49.643 --> 00:39:50.789
what's your relationship?

00:39:52.873 --> 00:39:54.608
Me and Jaehee?

00:39:55.950 --> 00:39:57.182
We were...

00:40:01.181 --> 00:40:02.659
everything to each other.

00:40:03.184 --> 00:40:04.486
Everything.

00:40:06.374 --> 00:40:08.589
Hey, I know you're in there!

00:40:10.884 --> 00:40:11.959
Hey!

00:40:18.507 --> 00:40:20.338
Hello, Yun Bia.

00:40:25.287 --> 00:40:26.362
Don't you know me?

00:40:27.339 --> 00:40:28.566
Hey, hey, hey!

00:40:29.268 --> 00:40:30.343
Gym clothes.

00:40:31.563 --> 00:40:33.276
I'm Sul Jaehee from the next class

00:40:33.311 --> 00:40:35.116
I borrowed gym clothes from you.

00:40:35.201 --> 00:40:36.276
From me?

00:40:38.213 --> 00:40:38.953
Here.

00:40:38.972 --> 00:40:40.436
I don't need them anymore.

00:40:40.747 --> 00:40:42.180
Hey!

00:40:44.089 --> 00:40:45.674
Yun Bia.

00:40:49.532 --> 00:40:50.908
Want to have chicken together?

00:40:54.465 --> 00:40:56.256
Hey, Bia, open the door!

00:40:57.636 --> 00:40:58.873
Bia!

00:41:01.546 --> 00:41:02.796
Do you like comics?

00:41:15.431 --> 00:41:17.096
Please just go away...

00:41:22.921 --> 00:41:24.326
Let's talk.

00:41:38.631 --> 00:41:41.486
She came to see me
every single day without fail.

00:41:42.421 --> 00:41:43.703
Both Jaehee and I

00:41:44.262 --> 00:41:46.106
came into this world alone.

00:41:48.981 --> 00:41:52.650
After my parents died,
I couldn't leave the house.

00:41:53.464 --> 00:41:56.721
Whenever I saw people,
I heard strange noises.

00:41:57.276 --> 00:41:59.116
And I'd faint immediately.

00:42:00.981 --> 00:42:04.376
At first, I couldn't be with
Jaehee for more than five minutes.

00:42:05.190 --> 00:42:06.714
Those five minutes

00:42:07.039 --> 00:42:08.698
became ten minutes,

00:42:09.023 --> 00:42:10.236
thirty minutes,

00:42:11.089 --> 00:42:13.388
and then an hour like this.

00:42:15.392 --> 00:42:17.166
I practiced with Jaehee.

00:42:18.032 --> 00:42:20.366
Thanks to him,
I could come out into the world.

00:42:24.441 --> 00:42:26.676
Jaehee made this for me too.

00:42:27.111 --> 00:42:28.752
So I wouldn't be in danger.

00:42:30.177 --> 00:42:31.252
For my sake.

00:42:33.943 --> 00:42:35.638
But you don't need that anymore.

00:42:36.295 --> 00:42:38.606
Gosh, you're lucky, Yun Bia.

00:42:39.501 --> 00:42:41.826
You've got a watch that never breaks.

00:42:45.477 --> 00:42:46.552
Where?

00:42:48.600 --> 00:42:49.675
Where?

00:42:49.994 --> 00:42:51.069
Show me.

00:42:51.570 --> 00:42:53.011
It's right in front of you.

00:42:53.246 --> 00:42:54.351
A handsome watch.

00:42:57.067 --> 00:42:59.282
Aren't you embarrassed
saying that yourself?

00:42:59.405 --> 00:43:00.092
Oh!

00:43:00.325 --> 00:43:02.033
You admitted it.
Right?

00:43:03.140 --> 00:43:04.255
What are you saying?

00:43:04.731 --> 00:43:06.791
Even though you'll disappear someday.

00:43:09.990 --> 00:43:11.065
Give me your hand.

00:43:11.991 --> 00:43:13.066
Why?

00:43:13.681 --> 00:43:14.766
Give me your hand.

00:43:15.360 --> 00:43:16.966
Gosh, seriously...

00:43:25.838 --> 00:43:26.838
Hey.

00:43:26.911 --> 00:43:28.126
What are you doing?

00:43:28.151 --> 00:43:29.846
Just stay still for a moment.

00:43:34.084 --> 00:43:35.159
Hmm?

00:43:45.438 --> 00:43:46.438
Tada!

00:43:48.901 --> 00:43:50.165
If someday

00:43:50.190 --> 00:43:52.586
I can't be by your side, don't worry.

00:43:54.337 --> 00:43:57.102
This will protect you in my place.

00:43:58.694 --> 00:43:59.879
You'll be okay.

00:44:10.290 --> 00:44:11.365
See,

00:44:11.880 --> 00:44:14.526
chasing around like that makes you tired.

00:44:30.721 --> 00:44:32.597
What's he talking about? "Handsome?"

00:45:13.721 --> 00:45:14.846
Was I asleep?

00:45:15.071 --> 00:45:15.922
Yeah.

00:45:15.941 --> 00:45:17.146
You were even snoring.

00:45:17.350 --> 00:45:19.324
C'mon...
No way...

00:45:21.049 --> 00:45:22.266
I need to use the bathroom.

00:45:31.777 --> 00:45:33.476
What's this?

00:45:38.771 --> 00:45:40.146
What is this?

00:45:45.501 --> 00:45:46.576
Is there no mirror?

00:45:47.205 --> 00:45:48.346
Let me see.

00:46:16.782 --> 00:46:17.589
Oh.

00:46:18.617 --> 00:46:19.836
I didn't even realize...

00:47:12.641 --> 00:47:13.716
Hello.